Name: Key
About the game: Key is a Hydra Labyrinth: With each level won, the maze gets bigger and harder. - Beat 100 levels in normal mode. - Enjoy pixel art graphics with 2D graphic lighting visual effects . - Listen to relaxing music and comfortable sounds while playing. - Beat 100 levels in hard mode . - Beat 10 levels in christmas mode . - Find 4 hidden Gems . Game Time: 20 Hours. Will you be able to help our hero find the key before the time is up? FEATURES Gems! Push! Boots, Map and Stair/Teleport! Have fun playing and relaxing in Key
